e themselves with bones."}, {"version": "white-2", "text": "They fly in circles around the sky. When they spot prey, they attack and carry it back to their nest with ease."}, {"version": "x", "text": "They fly in circles around the sky. When they spot prey, they attack and carry it back to their nest with ease."}, {"version": "y", "text": "Watching from the sky, they swoop to strike weakened Pok\u00e9mon on the ground. They decorate themselves with bones."}], "entryGameVersions": ["alpha-sapphire", "black", "black-2", "moon", "omega-ruby", "shield", "sun", "sword", "ultra-moon", "ultra-sun", "white", "white-2", "x", "y"], "moveGameGroups": ["black-2-white-2", "black-white", "omega-ruby-alpha-sapphire", "scarlet-violet", "sun-moon", "sword-shield", "ultra-sun-ultra-moon", "x-y"], "evolutionRows": [{"stage": 1, "name": "vullaby"}, {"stage": 2, "name": "mandibuzz"}]}